                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus from="71v" to="72r">ff. 71v-72r</locus>
                           <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">Protective prayer against snake bites (?).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                             በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡
                              ፩አምላክ፡ አመ፡ ይመጽዕ፡ እግዚዕነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ውስተ፡ ማሕጸና፡ ለድንግል፡ ማርያም፡ አርዌ፡
                              ተከይደ፡ ወዲያብሎስ፡ ተሰደ፡ ወለስሐ፡ ህምዙ፡ ለመልአከ፡ ሞት፡…</q>
                           
                           <note> Written in a recent secondary hand, with blue ballpoint pen.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1"> <desc>Corrections written over erasures: e.g., <locus target="#12v">12v</locus>, 14r, 24v, 31v, 36v.</desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2"><desc>Omitted letters
                           or words written interlineally: <locus target="#27v">27v</locus>, 49v,
                           55r, 58r, 61v.</desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc> Lacunae (space for rubricated names left unfilled):
                           the name of the donor/owner is missing throughout the Ms.: e.g., <locus target="#3v">3v</locus>, 4r, 4v, 5r, 6r.</desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e4"><desc>The word taʾammǝr is
                           marked by dashes above and below: <locus target="#66r">66r</locus>.</desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e5"><desc>Scribbles and doodles: e.g., <locus target="#18r">18r</locus>, 26r,
                           35v, 38r.</desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e6"><desc> Library note (?) written with blue ballpoint pen
                           containing the date <date>6/12/2000</date> on <locus target="#1v">1v</locus>.</desc></item>
                     </list>
